11#ifndef API_NETEQ_CUSTOM_NETEQ_FACTORY_H_
12#define API_NETEQ_CUSTOM_NETEQ_FACTORY_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15
16#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_decoder_factory.h"
17#include "api/neteq/neteq_controller_factory.h"
18#include "api/neteq/neteq_factory.h"
19#include "api/scoped_refptr.h"
20#include "system_wrappers/include/clock.h"
21
22namespace webrtc {
23
24// This factory can be used to generate NetEq instances that make use of a
25// custom NetEqControllerFactory.
26class CustomNetEqFactory : public NetEqFactory {
27 public:
28 explicit CustomNetEqFactory(
29 std::unique_ptr<NetEqControllerFactory> controller_factory);
30 ~CustomNetEqFactory() override;
31 CustomNetEqFactory(const CustomNetEqFactory&) = delete;
32 CustomNetEqFactory& operator=(const CustomNetEqFactory&) = delete;
33
34 std::unique_ptr<NetEq> CreateNetEq(
35 const NetEq::Config& config,
36 const rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioDecoderFactory>& decoder_factory,
37 Clock* clock) const override;
38
39 private:
40 std::unique_ptr<NetEqControllerFactory> controller_factory_;
41};
42
43} // namespace webrtc
44#endif // API_NETEQ_CUSTOM_NETEQ_FACTORY_H_
